subject: College Athletics
Basketball
Women and Girls
lead_paragraph: Homesick and fighting injuries, Kelsey Griffin considered leaving school. Instead she is the Big 12 Player of the Year and the Cornhuskers are a N.C.A.A. No. 1 seed.
